Heat a wok until hot and add the oil.Add all the spices and the ginger and stir-fry for one minute until fragrant.Add the potatoes and stir to coat in the spices.Add the stock and bring to a gentle simmer. Simmer for 10-15 minutes until the potatoes are tender.Stir in the tomatoes and coriander.Season with salt and freshly ground black pepper and serve.